cu.explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) will cause F1 connection establishment failures.

du.explanation_en: Changing the global log level from a string to a number will cause type validation errors during DU configuration parsing.
du.explanation_zh: 將全域日誌級別從字串改為數字會在 DU 配置解析期間造成類型驗證錯誤。
